text: New Girl is an American television sitcom set in Los Angeles. It began on September 20, 2011 and is shown on Star World Comedy Central Fox. It stars Zooey Deschanel as Jess Day, a teacher who moves in with three young men she meets on the Internet after separating from her partner with whom she lived. == Other websites == * *Official website Category:2011 American television series debuts Category:2018 American television series endings Category:2010s American sitcoms Category:2010s romance television series Category:English- language television programs Category:Romantic comedy television series Category:Television series about friendship Category:Television series set in Los Angeles Category:Star World India programmes Category:Comedy Central personalities Category:English television
